docker run              # run a new container instance from an image, if image not found, download auto
* -it --rm [image]      # temporary, interactive container
* -it [image]           # interactive container
* -dt [image]           # detached container, used most of the time
docker images           # list images
docker ps               # list containers
* -a                    # list all containers
* -s                    # list started containers
docker exec -it [container] [cmd] # connect to a computer
docker rm [container]   # delete container
docker rmi [image]      # delete image

Notes
dockerfile (blueprint) -> image
